span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　年纪少小朱重八谋求生存乏手段幸亏乡邻心肠热\r\n时常接济赏碗饭<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　介绍送进皇觉寺为饱肚腹将身蜷主持封仓断供给\r\n迫其乞讨整三年<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　再回寺庙朱元璋悟出世道需改变元末农民大起义\r\n遍地开花讯如电<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　胸怀大志伟丈夫造反念头如电闪毅然投奔郭子兴\r\n拼死他要搏一番<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　起初充当小角色帐下亲兵听吆唤由于出身甚寒微\r\n各种苦难全尝遍<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　故而无论做何事尽力侍奉极勤勉上阵杀敌肯拼命\r\n行军作战更勇敢<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　独具慧眼郭子兴料定此人不一般便将义女马秀英\r\n配他为妻以拢贤<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　新郎果不负众望打下二州及定远同时广泛揽英才\r\n荣擢总兵掌印钤<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　属下献上一计划对其未来很关键畅言古今成霸业\r\n必先割据占地盘<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　目标瞄准集庆路可扼南北要津涵时机成熟渡大江\r\n动作迅速急如箭<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　首先夺取太平路溧阳溧水顺手牵外围战场清理罢\r\n打通金陵大门扇<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　不料兵至秦淮河形势竟然现逆转非但坚城未拿下\r\n连折爱将心胆寒<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　时间飞逝又一载失利经验牢借鉴再攻集庆朱元璋\r\n战争策略已更换<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　攻取高地斗元军终把关键胜局奠措施得当巧运用\r\n节节进击无阻拦<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　元朝统帅名福寿面临危局心不甘有序退守凤凰台\r\n企图顽抗把势挽<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　欲凭坚城与固垒困兽犹斗待外援余勇可贾农民军\r\n趁势将其消灭干<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　自此而后朱元璋身价成倍往上翻仰仗强大根据地\r\n频发号令治东南<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　弃用国公赫吴王敢与诸侯比并肩巩固集庆大后方\r\n更名应天隐内涵<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　此时倒元势头猛举国烈焰怒放绽正有两股红巾军\r\n抗击铁骑苦征战<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　黄河下游地区广牵制敌手赖刘韩徐陈二位斗顽寇\r\n扬子流域步步艰<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　如此态势极有利坐享免费保卫线得便趁手朱元璋\r\n巧妙寻得空隙衔<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　自身实力益壮大攻城掠地把漏拣囊括江浙大部分\r\n兵锋远远略南皖<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　与岁俱增更兴盛益把自己羽翼添选贤任能朱元璋\r\n谦和待士甚恭谦<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　纷至沓来谋士多尽皆饱学极干练叶琛章溢刘伯温\r\n更有朱升与宋濂<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　其中朱升最出众一项建议极高瞻砌筑城墙莫厌高\r\n广积粮草多多善<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　缓称王霸避众目隐身遁形行藏潜三条策略真聪明\r\n每为后世效典范<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　至正廿年陈友谅率领大军来进犯一路攻陷太平府\r\n直抵应天形势险<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　仓促抵抗朱元璋屡次败阵忙慌乱多赖山桥两战役\r\n勉强才把危局扳<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　时间倥偬又三载西征大军卷狂澜两强相会鄱阳湖\r\n舍命搏杀战犹酣<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　不幸中箭陈友亮其子归降受招安带回金陵封汉王\r\n养尊处优效刘禅<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　再发精兵朱元璋仅隔五年时短暂大战对手张士诚\r\n胜胜负负各参半<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　前后连续两载余损兵折将难估算最后终于得胜利\r\n攻破平江心力殚<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　负伤遭擒张士成押解应天横祸惨挨尽多少无情杖\r\n浑身上下皮肉烂<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　竺桥桥面动大刑死后墓押鬼道魇重叠层层小白塔\r\n墨黑香炉把纸梵<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　至正廿七又出手恩威并济使双拳扩大地域用良谋\r\n温台二州入视线<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　恐吓逼降方国珍免动干戈耍手腕继而进军入闽广\r\n吞并疆域再拓展<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　称帝障碍有一个近在滁州很讨厌当时统帅红巾军\r\n最高领导真碍眼<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　该人名叫韩林儿必先除之方称愿思来想去有良策\r\n定计前去行欺骗<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　大张旗鼓去迎接诡称应天把事参信以为真韩林儿\r\n以为好事在眼前<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　行至六合步瓜镇恰在滔滔大江边故意唆人推岸落\r\n溺毙阎殿惨呼冤<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　此事一出众瞠目主家本性已叛反从来谋就天下者\r\n哪个本性不刁钻<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　猛将徐达去扫北顺帝望风忙逃窜面南称尊朱元璋\r\n国号大明都应天<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　初到金陵朱元璋统治中心几变换曾征王姓一府第\r\n充作指挥之军辕<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　铁冠道人与刘基经过研究细推演提出建议很具体\r\n皇城位定钟山南<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　明代兴建金陵城规模宏大甚伟岸二十一年历经久\r\n经历漫漫长时间<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　巨砖砌就坚无比史无前例坚城垣所用材料极考究\r\n规格统一标准严<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　建城巨砖需求急工部驻军齐动员整个一座应天府\r\n热火朝天忙不闲<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　处处闻听打坯声逢阴驱湿挥羽扇各处广泛建烧窑\r\n昼夜熊熊喷烈焰<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　远至长江中下游连亘五省全动弹三十府尹受责成\r\n哪敢小觑和轻慢<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　无不将此烧砖令当成首要事一件上传下达发号召\r\n一百州县起烽烟<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　大量城砖烧制妥块块需经细查检侧面刻有名和姓\r\n倘出差错难隐瞒<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　无论官员与工匠上上下下一绳栓次品退回重烧制\r\n再不合格便法办<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　所有涉及此事者个个小心惊颤颤生怕出得半点错\r\n不敢疏忽和偷懒<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　巨大城砖烧好后交给专门提调官质量数量必保证\r\n还得再次细检验<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　嗣后还需精储运水路解京装货船当时宽阔江面上\r\n货轮穿梭高扬帆<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　巨砖不惟建都城其他用途也广泛官署祠庙和陵墓\r\n如法砌筑也普遍<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　建城所需巧工匠全国范围广招揽东山名家属张宁\r\n无锡二陆排在先<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　搬搬运运苦劳力强行征调二十万流民罪犯与俘虏\r\n被迫服役更无算<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　建城所需费用巨江南富户均分摊霸道官府拨数字\r\n实行分段大包干<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　捐献最多头一位乃是苏州沈万三半劈金陵有其一\r\n说来此事万古罕<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　传说修建南门时竟然屡建屡塌坍人传沈家聚宝盆\r\n能把此祸巧禳免<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　马上下令朱元璋立即征用莫迟延深深埋入地基下\r\n当真功成墙高攒<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　如此巨额捐助多反给沈某招祸端生性多疑朱元璋\r\n令其进京如圈圈<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　伺后枉加莫须有财产罚没戍边关明朝刑部大天牢\r\n既是其家私花园<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　大明应天设计巧采用独特怪方案不按常规呈方形\r\n唯据地势法自然<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　规划严谨分数步建新改旧筑城垣三竖高墙开街道\r\n第四砌造最外延<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　身负圣命刘伯温皇城位置细踏勘经过测量方位准\r\n定于钟山龙头前<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　各个方面合要求但是依然有缺陷地基正压前湖水\r\n难扼碧波涌狂澜<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　只好调集人无数搬石挑土来平填在这痛苦过程中\r\n坑杀苦命田德满<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　谐音好名求吉兆活脱老汉投深潭嗣后夜夜魂梦闹\r\n无奈追谥封神仙<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　填湖虽使表面平但做地基仍嫌软如果措施不得当\r\n最终还得要塌陷<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　城墙底部承力重排摆巨石做铺垫宫殿下面夯木桩\r\n确保皇族举家安<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　最为神奇聚宝门坚墙兀立难登攀瓮城战时供防守\r\n进出掌握主动权<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　内外共计设两道平时开启有时限厚厚实实千斤闸\r\n一旦落下牢如焊<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　布有独特藏军洞里端密封实砖券军事物资长存放\r\n战时取用极方便<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　纷纷繁繁数十个可隐士兵达三千遍观举世各城池\r\n绝无仅有确罕见<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,25