mily:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　能工巧匠十万人个有特长技精湛大多汇聚十八坊\r\n地点潮湿又阴暗<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　突发奇想朱洪武来个人口大调换认为元代遗留民\r\n不甚可靠需驱撵<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　大都迁往云南去数量众多难数点据说他们到如今\r\n仍把金陵旧习延<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　往迁南京极不易悉心挑拣设档案必须马上有用处\r\n利于建设促发展<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　另挟富豪阔财主强制迁来带资产都城渐渐被充盈\r\n人口达到四十万<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span s