n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　接替二丑璞鼎查殖民老手极凶悍观其罪恶发迹史\r\n双手满把鲜血染<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　前任失败有教训认真总结换手段军事占领意义小\r\n至关重要取主权<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　满族清朝大帝国政治腐败极糜烂对内独裁血镇压\r\n对外屈辱献媚谄<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　多年鸦片输进去`倒无数精壮汉打疼之后拿东西\r\n要想拦挡看谁敢<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　忘形得意璞鼎查摊开海图细观览目标瞄向扬子江\r\n觅然惊出一身汗<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);f