span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　趁着士气尚锐利利在速战莫迟缓决定兵发扬子江\r\n去把南京城攻占<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　孤注一掷下赌注倘胜得利万万番预设目标功成日\r\n轻取京津若左券<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　派出大批传教士帮兵助阵把事干身披拖地黑大氅\r\n去将清军内情探<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　胸前挂着十字架高举圣经乱游窜不日之间有回报\r\n间谍作用确非凡<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　有一去处名镇江运河扬子汇合点自古兵家必争地\r\n交通便捷凭水旱<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, A