<div style=\"padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">康明著　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　鸦片战争痛失利国人心头受震撼各路英雄揭竿起\r\n抗击侵略反封建<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　太平天国声势壮义举金田洪秀全横跨四湖越三江\r\n再破武昌坚城垣<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　部队休整得补充继续开拔走泥丸浩浩荡荡百万军\r\n势如狂石击危卵<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　一路飞奔急向东赳赳水营抵下关历时不足一个月\r\n南京囊入包围圈<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　三月十九刚破晓南京城头雾漫漫骤起进攻太平军\r\n四面冲杀卷狂澜<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　惊天动地一声响烟尘滚滚乱石溅无比坚固凤仪门\r\n被炸登时裂两爿<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　蜂拥而入将士勇指挥有序不紊乱一路径奔鼓楼岗\r\n一路猛扑鸡笼山<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　遭逢清兵太平门双方拼杀开激战痛惜人数实在少\r\n退归又把旧途沿<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　一支英勇太平军浴血冲杀越成贤径扑要塞驻防营\r\n攻击地点很关键<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　倘若目标能达成牢攥制胜主动权身负使命极重要\r\n脚步匆匆急如箭<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　中途经过黄家圹遇队清兵正逃窜众人哄抬轿一乘\r\n左右摇晃颤颠颠<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　迎头撞见义军到尽皆麻溜卸重掮持枪卫队未抵抗\r\n撒腿如飞四下踮<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　轿内总督陆建瀛声势力竭急呼唤混蛋回来快救我\r\n过后老爷赏大钱<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　一见义军围上去立时晕眩身瘫痪刀光闪过人头落\r\n狗官蹬腿赴罗阎<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　两江总督被斩首消息风传讯如电有人高兴把掌鼓\r\n有人泪飞如涌泉<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　镇西守南清官兵丢盔卸甲将身潜义军鼓舞再乘勇\r\n全力又破门三扇<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　激烈战斗一日整仰仗东王有经验识破对手奸狡计\r\n处理事物甚果敢<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　一鼓作气不罢休全歼八旗兵三万南京全城皆攻取\r\n江宁将军被腰斩<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　义军夺取南京城再发精兵紧接衔两支劲旅齐头进\r\n遥相照应如双拳<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　金山瓜洲相继得镇江扬州旋即占东征胜利成果大\r\n后方巩固稳如磐<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　乘胜东进太平军披坚执锐无阻拦愁煞天王难抉择\r\n一件大事摆眼前<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　所有领袖齐参与俱为建都把论辩意见渐渐趋统一\r\n南京理应为首选<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　王气独盛帝王宅山川形胜举世罕经济发达物产丰\r\n矿藏铅铁富资源<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　军事位置更重要地理独特倚天堑进可征战夺天下\r\n退宜防守城池坚<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　太平天国各首领认真分析细踏勘利弊因素细衡量\r\n政治经济细调研<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　最后意见趋一致都选南京成定谳自从建立政权后\r\n义军进入新阶段<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　天王胸中有宏图力推事业再发展多路出击发攻势\r\n努力开辟新局面<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　北伐推倒清政府摧枯拉朽扫群顽西征大力开疆土\r\n以把地域拓更宽<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　北伐西征兵锋利内政建设也齐全天朝田亩好制度\r\n堪为国策举世赞<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　分地论醢慈丝诒曜济魅凡灰衅富志诺燃\r\n好次搭配明分辨<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　例如一家人六口仨好仨孬各参半丰产欠收两拉平\r\n公正无私不偏袒<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　如此作为显效益天国民众享饱暖有饭大家都有吃\r\n有衣大家都有穿<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　为民立极好制度符合劳动人意愿正大光明非空想\r\n轰轰烈烈付实践<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　军队夺占新领地管理跟进有创见设局抽税定粮口\r\n颁牌严把户籍编<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　整顿秩序定规章成绩昭彰更斐然鸦片毒害严令禁\r\n天朝明确颁条款<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　倘敢贩卖必斩首知情不举受株连铲除赌博丑积习\r\n违者即为把戒犯<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　公开禁止嫖娼妓北翼二王联名签不尊条款犯律者\r\n合家剿洗勿从宽<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　太平天国讲科学禁绝妇女把足缠放纵大脚自生长\r\n有利劳动与生产<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　文化建设更奇特方式独具真新鲜创立教会拜上帝\r\n履行程序很简单<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　礼拜尽在安息日闻钟赞神须恭谦朗诵奏章致敬意\r\n读罢脱手用火梵<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　清朝将士俱称妖决计尽除连根铲贬低孔孟呼邪教\r\n焚毁著作不准看<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　所到之处砸佛像融炼金身铸刀剑罗汉搬上雨花台\r\n充做标靶把兵练<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　唯一怪事难理解男女大防过谨严虽为恩爱好夫妻\r\n竟也隔离分榻眠<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　一旦发现违反者当真惩罚不恕免如此制度灭天性\r\n后人批评太极端<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　针对辖区工商业起初政策有弱点宣布废除私有制\r\n一切统归天王管<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　导致私企无出路纷纷弃城远搬迁物价起落不稳定\r\n制度只好做应变<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　卫戍警备极重要首都天京严防范水面路上城内外\r\n巧用地理好条件<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　颇具特色了望楼鹤立鸡群高高攒楼楼之间可对视\r\n层层上下有梯舷<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　望楼建上雨花台报恩寺塔比并肩常备色旗灯鼓角\r\n四周环绕红栏栅<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　每班五人轮值守从不懈怠不偷懒白天敌来挥旗号\r\n夜晚妖至色灯燃<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　清朝政府调大军围困天京扎营盘江南大营两万兵\r\n钦差向荣掌旗幡<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　江北大营势稍弱统管钦差名琦善两处大营如犄角\r\n夹击天京若双钳<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　太平天国统帅部破围军命速下颁兵撤西线秦日刚\r\n直奔江北把敌歼<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　将士接令齐奋勇利刃要将毒瘤剜继任琦善托明阿\r\n大败而逃一溜烟<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　调回猛将石达开痛击向荣外防线势如迅雷袭六城\r\n清军主力被牢牵<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　意欲截击秦日刚吉尔杭阿伏路畔枉为巡抚乏谋略\r\n兵败高资自了断<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　佯攻镇江造态势分兵向荣受蒙骗秦石二将攻势猛\r\n江南大营固守顽<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　东王急令开双门滚滚义军狂浪掀一举荡平孝陵卫\r\n天京危局转为安<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　晴天霹雳石流泪都城内乱自伤残专横跋扈杨秀清\r\n位高权重独专擅<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　稍有忤逆辄处死羞辱大将若等闲巧嘴妄说皇上帝\r\n杖责天王欲谋篡<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　天王密诏韦昌辉起兵讨伐平内患宅心仁厚屡告诫\r\n杀杨至亲莫过三<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　一旦功成株连广造虐祸首挨皮鞭伪装受刑钓余党\r\n再诛两万灭人寰<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　忍见残杀石达开耿耿忠心如油煎立见领袖陈利害\r\n再叩北府行规劝<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　哪知毒恶韦昌辉竟对翼王动邪念幸有预兆先知觉\r\n越城回营保平安<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　恼羞成怒韦昌辉诛石全家造惨案翼王发兵复仇恨\r\n天朝合力靖国难<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　生擒逆贼处极刑首级军门高挂I前后历时两月余\r\n血腥事件告一段<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　翼王义举得人心公推掌权撑危掾天王消极汲教训\r\n竟对忠臣加防范<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　安插亲信事牵制用人怀私提亲眷胸怀大志石达开\r\n毅然脱离洪集团<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　一场事变后果重由盛到衰势锐减义军大量被屠杀\r\n其中许多是骨干<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　分裂出走数万人大好局面呈逆转清廷趁机调大军\r\n天京再把困境陷<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　摆脱内讧烦恼多天王力将颓势挽领导核心被调整\r\n起用军师洪仁\<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　庸者虽亲削爵禄贤才擢用无私偏重封翼王石达开\r\n盼其从速把京返<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　敌手内乱清廷喜二营回击恶澜掀大举进攻犯皖北\r\n湘军首领曾国藩<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　如何化解此困厄后起之秀挑重担陈李二小共破敌\r\n义气不啻同生孪<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　太平天国建都后如日中天光灿灿西方殖民侵略者\r\n表示中立把誓宣<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　鸦片战争二度起津京条约忍辱签一朝得势诸列强\r\n面目狰狞现真颜<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　英夷何伯巴下礼狮口大开吐黏涎欲助灭清均沾利\r\n平分中国好大胆<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　恶鬼话音未落地天王盛怒把脸翻我起义军为救国\r\n尔等奸宄快滚蛋<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\"><br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(73,73,73);font-family:宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:25px;\">　　二鬼受挫提旧事依然想把便宜捡据理力争太平军\r\n驳斥旧约有时限<\/span><span style=\"backgro